    "algorithm_path": "case-identification",
    "algorithm_path_description": "Identifies the base population of patients on ACE inhibitor medications. Both cases (patients with ACEi-induced cough) and controls (patients on ACEi without cough) will have ACEi prescriptions. This tests whether LLMs can identify the correct RxNorm SCD codes for common ACE inhibitors.",
